        <h3 class="luxury-title-sub">🕒 Processing Window</h3>
        <p class="luxury-text-p">All successful orders undergo verification and fulfillment processing within <strong>24 business hours</strong>. Orders logged post 5:00 PM are queue-forwarded to the subsequent operational day.</p>
        
        <h3 class="luxury-title-sub">🗺️ Transit Timeline</h3>
        <p class="luxury-text-p">Standard logistics require <strong>3 to 5 business days</strong> for major metros and urban centers. Regional destination timelines may vary based on courier routing networks.</p>
        
        <h3 class="luxury-title-sub">💳 Payment Architecture</h3>
        <p class="luxury-text-p">We operate exclusively on a <strong>100% Prepaid-Only Model</strong>. Cash on Delivery (COD) is structurally unavailable. This policy preserves inventory exclusivity and ensures high-priority dispatch handling.</p>

